HEADWORD: Protopodite
<hw>Pro*top"o*dite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Proto-</ets> + Gr. <?/, <?/, foot.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
